platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: GoatZ poses a simple question: How long can you survive the apocalypse  as a zombie goat? This hilariously absurd follow-up to Goat Simulator takes tons of survival-game conventionslike crafting, time-based challenges, and a big, open worldand wraps them together in a package intentionally littered with glitches. As you make your way around town, licking trash cans and head-butting zombies, the ridiculous bugs and hysterical premise will have you laughing out loud. Its dumb fun in the best way.
